Bohn

For more than 50 years, Bohn has been a leader in products built for the supermarket, grocery store, restaurant and retail industries. Featuring a strong focus on innovation and the environment, Bohn offers cutting-edge technologies and outstanding efficiencies backed by world-class service and technical support. 
Bohn provides an unmatched selection of precisely engineered systems and responsive customer service. Whether you’re upgrading your current system, replacing old equipment or starting from the ground up, you can count on Bohn for reliable, quiet performance, as well as energy savings and lower overall operating costs. 
View a complete inventory of Bohn products and literature.




