Company Overview of Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC designs, manufactures, and sells commercial refrigeration products for food service, supermarkets, industry, and cold storage markets in the United States and internationally. It offers evaporators, condensers, merchandise display cases, unit coolers, compressorized products, and condensers and fluid coolers; products ranging from cold-food storage equipment for restaurants and retail stores to medical and pharmacy refrigeration to customized cooling systems for industrial and data facilities; and other refrigeration products. The company also provides factory installed control solutions that provide automatic superheat, room temperature, and intelligent ...
Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC designs, manufactures, and sells commercial refrigeration products for food service, supermarkets, industry, and cold storage markets in the United States and internationally. It offers evaporators, condensers, merchandise display cases, unit coolers, compressorized products, and condensers and fluid coolers; products ranging from cold-food storage equipment for restaurants and retail stores to medical and pharmacy refrigeration to customized cooling systems for industrial and data facilities; and other refrigeration products. The company also provides factory installed control solutions that provide automatic superheat, room temperature, and intelligent defrost control for refrigeration unit coolers. In addition, it offers commercial refrigeration parts, accessories, and electronic controls; and training services. The company offers its products through wholesalers and distributors, and online. Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Stone Mountain, Georgia. It has manufacturing facilities in Stone Mountain, Columbus, and Tifton, Georgia. The company has warehouses in Chino, California; and Dallas, Texas. Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC operates as a subsidiary of Heatcraft Inc.
