Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC: Evaporators









































Home » Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC: Evaporators

What's New
Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC: Evaporators



July 3, 2003



        Reprints
      



        No Comments
      


A stainless steel cabinet option and a stainless steel drain pan option are available on low- and medium-profile unit coolers, as well as center mounts and large unit coolers. The stainless steel evaporators are offered on Bohn, Larkin, Climate Control, and Chandler lines. The units are resistant to corrosion and are easy to clean, which results in an added sanitary feature, the company says. The stainless steel cabinet option is excellent for wine rooms, food processing, pharmaceuticals, biomedical, and other applications, states the manufacturer. The units include a stainless steel external cabinet, drain pan, hanger brackets, and external fasteners, all of which are constructed of 20-gauge stainless steel.


Heatcraft Refrigeration Products LLC, 2175 West Park Place Blvd., Stone Mountain, GA 30087; 770-465-5600; 770-465-5990 (fax); www.heatcraftrpd.com.







